### Create Source for HackerNews
POST http://localhost:3001/api/sources
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://news.ycombinator.com/news"
}

### Rebuild existing Source (triggers AI workflow, preserves usage_stats)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/sources
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://news.ycombinator.com/news",
  "rebuild": true
}

### "Load_More" site
